title: Jboy's Week 2 College Football Recap!
itunes:title: Jboy's Week 2 College Football Recap!
description:
Jboy breaks down a stacked week 2 in college football. He tells you why Oregon was able to upset Ohio State (5:30), why Arkansas dominated Texas (27:20) and much much more! Make sure to check us out LIVE on Youtube every day at 3pm EST, plus follow us @thejboyshow on all social media platforms!
